'''Throwing knives''' are a type of [[members]] [[Ranged]] throwing weapon. They can be [[poison]]ed and can be wielded with [[shield]]s or [[god book]]s for protection.

Throwing knives can be created via the [[Smithing]] skill, with the exception of black and dragon knives. Each bar will produce 5 throwing knives of the corresponding metal.

Throwing knives are among the fastest weapons in the game (along with [[dart]]s), and are commonly used for [[Player killing|PKing]] or training Ranged. They have an attack range of 4 tiles, 6 if using longrange.

